
== System requirements

Linux, Apple OS-X, and Solaris

Ruby 1.8.6 or higher and Rubygems 1.3.1 or higher

Outbound access via https

== Install scout gem

$ sudo gem install scout

== Install agent key from scoutapp.com

$ scout

[root@pmta01 ~]# /usr/local/bin/scout
=== Scout Installation Wizard ===

You need the Server Key displayed in the Server Settings tab.
It looks like:

  6ecad322-0d17-4cb8-9b2c-a12c4541853f

Enter the Server Key:
457f8c98-b637-4de4-bee0-63c0bc4318ea

Attempting to contact the server...
exit

Failed. 
For more help, please visit:

http://scoutapp.com/help



== Setup crontab file

If you are using the system crontab
(usually located at /etc/crontab):

****** START CRONTAB SAMPLE ******
* * * * *  root /usr/bin/scout 457f8c98-b637-4de4-bee0-63c0bc4318ea
******  END CRONTAB SAMPLE  ******

If you are using this current user's crontab
(using crontab -e to edit):

****** START CRONTAB SAMPLE ******
* * * * *  /usr/bin/scout 457f8c98-b637-4de4-bee0-63c0bc4318ea
******  END CRONTAB SAMPLE  ******
